name: The Octopus Warrior - NFT
description:
This is the animated digital version of our original artwork "The Octopus Warrior", available at www.greiflazic.com.

A colorful mind is a series of drawings made entirely with multiple layers of different color pencils. It is an exercise to explore our imagination. 

Colorful pencils on Hahnemühle bamboo paper 265 g/m2.

The Image of the artwork was isolated in layers and animated.
